    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/417109fbb78a58b994e7be9f5c66311d.avif?t=1767684936\" width=450 height=150 /></span><br><br><br>帮助村民建设村庄，重建城市。随着每一个新的水平，你的村庄都会发展壮大。为这些土地注入古老的生命！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7fd6200e2a8e59e58a07a90f973431df.poster.avif?t=1767684936\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7fd6200e2a8e59e58a07a90f973431df.webm?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7fd6200e2a8e59e58a07a90f973431df.mp4?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>帮助村民建设村庄，重建城市。随着每一个新的水平，你的村庄都会发展壮大。为这片土地注入古老的生命！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7a797c787cb654208aa59e0b15139098.poster.avif?t=1767684936\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7a797c787cb654208aa59e0b15139098.webm?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7a797c787cb654208aa59e0b15139098.mp4?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>您可以在 3 个岛屿上获得必要的资源。种植蔬菜、获取石头或砍柴。每个资源都会对您有用。有了它们，您可以改善建筑物、完成任务或在市场上出售它们。这一切都取决于你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/0ac20204fac5d5ee18c6665e6ee8cc0b.poster.avif?t=1767684936\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/0ac20204fac5d5ee18c6665e6ee8cc0b.webm?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/0ac20204fac5d5ee18c6665e6ee8cc0b.mp4?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>重建完村庄后，整个城市将向您开放！我想你知道如何处理它。这就是您如何将一个小村庄带入整个岛屿，而不仅仅是一个岛屿。任何事情都可能发生<br><br><br><strong>酒吧和钓鱼</strong><br><br>买一根鱼竿去当地的池塘钓鱼。渔获物也可以出售并获得几枚金币。您可以安全地将它们留给当地的调酒师。他是村里最早的人之一，已经盖起了自己的房子。我不知道他为什么不帮助别人，但这已经不重要了。<br>最主要的是，他可以在悦耳的音乐和一杯甜食中讲几个故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7fd6200e2a8e59e58a07a90f973431df.poster.avif?t=1767684936\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7fd6200e2a8e59e58a07a90f973431df.webm?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174460/extras/7fd6200e2a8e59e58a07a90f973431df.mp4?t=1767684936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
